# Security

- Plugin permissions default deny.
- No arbitrary shell/network/filesystem/credentials/clipboard without explicit grant.
- No telemetry; no secret access in scaffold.
- Legacy VSIX bridge isolated, never default, never before first paint.
- Workspace Trust Plus before executing workspace-owned tools.
